  <title translate="true">Usage Examples</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Usage Examples</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading 2"><anchor id="example_1" styleclass="Heading 2"><keywords><keyword translate="true">Issue example</keyword><keyword translate="true">Using section boxes</keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="Heading 2" translate="true">Using 3D Controls to Create Issues</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading 3"><text styleclass="Heading 3" translate="true">Example 1</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Procedure Heading"><text styleclass="Procedure Heading" translate="true">To create an issue using section cut:</text></para>
    <list id="106" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Procedure" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Procedure" translate="true">Launch your model and go to the </text><text styleclass="GUI_item" translate="true">3D</text><text styleclass="Procedure" translate="true"> view (top menu option).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Procedure" translate="true">Walk to a place where the issue is located. You can go to a specific object, room etc. For example, let us navigate to a room (living room).</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="living_room.png" scale="50.00%" width="794" height="400" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="106" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Procedure" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Procedure" translate="true">Then let us create a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Model-Elements-and-Controls" anchor="section" styleclass="Procedure" translate="true">section</link><text styleclass="Procedure" translate="true"> (</text><image src="section_ico.png" scale="80.00%" width="46" height="26" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> icon) here. For example, let us cut the side wall of the room using the </text><text styleclass="GUI_item" translate="true">Plane</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> mode of the section tool.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="section_plan_example.png" scale="50.00%" width="792" height="404" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="106" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Procedure" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Then save the section as a viewpoint (the viewpoint icon at the bottom of the screen). This step is optional, if you just need to create an issue.</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Now you can navigate to the newest viewpoint and create an </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Issue-LifeCycle-report_issue" anchor="new_3d_issue" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">issue</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> containing the create section cut ( click </text><image src="new_issue_ico.png" scale="80.00%" width="54" height="30" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">). </text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Heading 3"><text styleclass="Heading 3" translate="true">Example 2.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Procedure Heading"><text styleclass="Procedure Heading" translate="true">To create a section section box:</text></para>
    <list id="107" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Procedure" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Walk/navigate to the spot where you have to create an issue</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. </text></li>
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Create a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Model-Elements-and-Controls" anchor="section" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">section</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> using the </text><text styleclass="GUI_item" translate="true">Box</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> mode. In the figure below you can see how a box containing a table is created. </text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center;"><image src="section_box_example.png" scale="50.00%" width="694" height="388" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <list id="107" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Procedure" style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Create a viewpoint with your section box (optional step).</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Procedure"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Click </text><image src="new_issue_ico.png" scale="80.00%" width="54" height="30" styleclass="Image Caption"></image><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to create an issue</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. Use markup tools to highlight key points.</text></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="img_display"><image src="issue_example.png" scale="50.00%" width="796" height="402" styleclass="img_display"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Procedure"></para>
  </body>
